<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٦٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٦٠٤٢ - ابْنُ أَبِي زَائِدَةَ، عَنِ ابْنِ عَوْنٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ مُحَمَّدٍ قَالَ:</span> قَالَ عُمَرُ: <span class="c2">«مَنْ يَعْلَمْ مَا يَحِلُّ لِلْمَمْلُوكِ مِنَ النِّسَاءِ؟»</span> قَالَ رَجُلٌ: أَنَا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَمْ؟»</span> قَالَ: امْرَأَتَيْنِ، فَسَكَتَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>